earthquakes-feed — attribution notice
=====================================

This dataset aggregates publicly available earthquake parameters from multiple
seismic networks. Per-event attribution is preserved in every Feature under
properties.feed.provenance[]. Please keep the attributions below when redistributing.

- U.S. Geological Survey (ANSS ComCat) (DOI: 10.5066/F7MS3QZH)
- EMSC/CSEM, https://www.emsc-csem.org
- GEOFON Program, GFZ German Research Centre for Geosciences (DOI: 10.14470/TR560404)
- Istituto Nazionale di Geofisica e Vulcanologia (INGV) (DOI: 10.13127/iside)
- GeoNet (GNS Science / Toka Tū Ake EQC), New Zealand
- RESIF / Réseau Sismologique et géodésique Français (DOI: 10.15778/RESIF.FR)
- National Observatory of Athens (NOA), Institute of Geodynamics

